  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Valsaa Alpinresort is a superb, all-inclusive adults-only hotel with extensive facilities. Conveniently located, the hotel is just a few minutes walk from the village centre and Schattberg X-press lift.</p>
<h2>All-inclusive luxury</h2>
<p>At the Valsaa Alpinresort guests have complete flexibility when it comes to meals - eat &amp; drink when you want, with food available in the hotel restaurant from breakfast until dinner. Don’t plan your day around meals, plan your meals around your day.</p>
<p>With Premium All-Inclusive drinks are included from 8am to midnight each day. On the menu are beers, wines, spirits and soft drinks, plus sparkling wines and cocktails too.</p>
<p>Breakfast starts early and finishes late. After brunch, there's lunch, and then afternoon snacks. A four-course dinner in the evenings completes the day.</p>
<h2>Head-to-toe pampering in the AlpinSPA</h2>
<p>Whether it's a workout or relaxation that you're after, a visit to the huge AlpinSPA is perfect for a bit of self-care. Swim a few lengths of the 25-metre heated outdoor sports pool, or relax in the whirlpools. Take in the views from the Panorama Lawn, or soak in the silence of the relaxation room.<br />Find a remedy for tired muscles in the Sauna World. Finnish and organic saunas, an infrared cabin, a steam room, and an outdoor textile (swimsuits permitted) sauna will help ease the aches and have you ready to explore again tomorrow.</p>
<p>This hotel is adults-only and therefore children under 16 years old are not permitted.</p>]]></description>
