  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h4><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.saalbach.com/en/summer/joker-card" target="_blank"></a><strong>Joker Card partner accommodation</strong></h4>
<p>When you book the Valsaa Alpinresort, the <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.saalbach.com/en/summer/joker-card" target="_blank">Joker Card</a> is included in your holiday meaning you can enjoy unlimited use of up to six gondolas in Saalbach Hinterglemm, up to ten guided walks per week and much more.</p>
<p><strong>Spa &amp; wellness facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Indoor swimming pool</li>
<li>Outdoor swimming pool</li>
<li>Two outdoor whirlpools</li>
<li>Finnish sauna</li>
<li>Organic sauna</li>
<li>Infrared sauna</li>
<li>Textile sauna cabin</li>
<li>Brine steam room</li>
<li>Relaxation area</li>
<li>Gym</li>
<li>Spa &amp; massage treatments (payable locally)</li>
<li>Pool towels</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Additional facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Sun terrace</li>
<li>Parking</li>
<li>Garage (payable locally)</li>
</ul>
<p>Please note, this is an adults only hotel (minimum age 16 years).</p>]]></facilityDescription>
