  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Double Rooms</strong> are around 31m² and sleep two to three using a single sofa bed or extra bed in the seating area. These modern-styled rooms also have a balcony. The box-spring beds can be separated.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> offer the most space at around 36m² and sleep two to four using a double sofa bed. Also with a seating area and balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Single Superior Rooms</strong> are around 31m² and have a seating area.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Mini fridge (unstocked)</li>
<li>Bathrobes</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in:<strong> 4pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out: <strong>11am</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>This hotel is adults-only and therefore children under 16 years old are not permitted.</p>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tourist tax of approx. €2.95 per person per night is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
